Actor Vuyo Ngcukane has remembered his mother 21 years after her death. The star paid tribute to his mother, saying she was his best friend. In an emotionally charged Twitter message, he said he misses her every day. Tweed the actor: "Today marks 21 years since I lost my best friend, my cheerleader, comforter, the epitome of love, generosity and kindness, I carry everything she was in my heart, I love and miss you everyday Mama Heart suit? His girlfriend Renate Stuurman commented with a heart emoji.